                        <input type="radio" name="usability" value="5">5</label>
                </p>
            </fieldset>

            <fieldset class="visuals">
                <p>From a scale of 1-5 with 1 being the worst and 5 being the best, how would you rate this websites visual appeal and design?
                    <br />
